title: Immigrant shot, killed in St. Paul remembered as loving dad
text: ST. PAUL, Minn. (AP) - A Karen (keh-REHN') immigrant who was fatally shot outside his St. Paul home is being remembered as a loving father. The Star Tribune (http://strib.mn/1jXxZr4 ) reports more than 100 family and friends gathered Saturday to celebrate the life of 54-year-old Htoo Baw. Baw was gunned ... ...
